/**
 * MantTeq Website JavaScript API Documentation
 * 
 * This file contains all the interactive functionality for the MantTeq website.
 */

/**
 * CAROUSEL COMPONENT
 * 
 * Features:
 * - Auto-advancing slides
 * - Manual navigation controls
 * - Touch support for mobile
 * - Keyboard navigation
 * - Indicator dots
 * 
 * Methods:
 * nextSlide()       - Advances to next slide
 * prevSlide()       - Goes to previous slide
 * goToSlide(index)  - Jumps to specific slide
 * resetAutoSlide()  - Resets the auto-advance timer
 */

/**
 * SERVICE MODALS
 * 
 * Features:
 * - Dynamic loading based on service clicked
 * - Click outside to close
 * - Escape key to close
 * - Accessible focus management
 * 
 * Methods:
 * Modal opens when service button clicked
 * Modal closes with X button or outside click
 */

/**
 * FAQ ACCORDION
 * 
 * Features:
 * - Only one item open at a time
 * - Smooth animations
 * - Accessible ARIA attributes
 */

/**
 * FORM HANDLING
 * 
 * Features:
 * - Client-side validation
 * - Success/error messages
 * - Loading states
 * - Integration with Formspree
 */

/**
 * PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATIONS
 * 
 * Implemented:
 * - Lazy loading images
 * - Debounced scroll events
 * - Critical CSS inlined
 * - Non-critical CSS deferred
 * - Service worker caching
 * - Minimized JavaScript
 */